PART 5 — Plugins

Plugins extend Maven functionality.

Examples:

compile code,
run programs,
package JARs.
Maven Compiler Plugin

Your notes are correct here.

Add Plugin
<build>

    <plugins>

        <plugin>

            <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>

            <artifactId>maven-compiler-plugin</artifactId>

            <version>3.8.1</version>

            <configuration>

                <source>1.8</source>

                <target>1.8</target>

            </configuration>

        </plugin>

    </plugins>

</build>
Meaning
Tag	Meaning
source	Java source version
target	JVM target version
